codes.code: argmax 'This is a quiz of your ability to understand latin grammar. For each problem there is a ~ character in the text and your job is to figure out what word should be replaced by the ~. Provide the answer only. Quī ab amīcīs proficīsc~ laet~ nōn potest. Choose from this set of possible answers [ entur iuntur, untur, itur, itur ētur untur itur, ī ārī, itur ārī] [ANSWER]' from 'openai/text-ada-001' where ANSWER in [ 'entur iuntur', 'untur', 'itur', 'itur ētur untur itur', 'ī ārī', 'itur ārī']
